page.title: 09ECOLOGY
page.content: {COMMON} Daisy,Buttercup,Dandelion,Ivy,Stinging Nettles. {REASONABLY COMMON} Groundsel,Foxglove,Honeysuckle,Greater Stitchwort,Scarlet Pimpernel. {RARE Cowslip. {FLOWERLESS Mares Tail,Dock,Plantain.{ {FLOWERS Ladies Smock,Red Campion,Forget_Me_ Not,Dog Violet,Ground Ivy. {VISIT TO THE MEADOW} On the 13th of June 1985 we visited a meadow which belonged to Mr. Weetman. The meadow is the only one in our grid area which hasn't been sprayed with chemicals for over 70 years.It has about 70 to 75 different species of wild flowers. {BY GAIL DENNING & ANGELA IVES.}
